  </div>




</a></div>
    
  <div class="teaser-date">04/15/14</div>
  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/april-2014/ten-things-you-might-not-know-about-particle-accelerators?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span>Ten things you might not know about particle accelerators</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>From accelerators unexpectedly beneath your feet to a ferret that once cleaned accelerator components, <em>Symmetry</em> shares some lesser-known facts about particle accelerators.</p>


</article>
</div>
